package has no canonical ordering of the fit's latent objects.}

\item{\code{scores(x, domain = NULL)}}{Required by
\code{score_stability}. For oneblock shapes the \code{domain} argument
is optional. For cross shapes it must accept \code{"X"} or \code{"Y"}.
